ass=\"red\">日美外交和防務部門高官4日舉行了視頻會談，明確表示強烈反對在東海和南海憑藉武力和強制力單方面改變現狀的嘗試，共享了對中國《海警法》的強烈關切。</span><br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">日美擬本月中旬召開外長和防長出席的安全保障磋商委員會（2+2會議）</span>，此次的高官會談中可能也就此展開了協調。<br />\n<br />\n  參加會談的美方官員有副助理國務卿卡納佩（Marc Knapper）等人，日方則為外務省北美局參事官有馬裕、防衛省防衛政策局次長大和太郎。雙方確認將為維持自由開放的印度太平洋以及加強威懾力和日美同盟而緊密合作。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2021/03/e3fb3ae736df.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2Fe3fb3ae736df.html&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=4d8578df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2021/03/e3fb3ae736df.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d12bc7a69f28f414059917a7693c8350f09591d","tid":2433781,"uid":155095,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bzDcx22q9_9uR0IOjwTDEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjguODA4NTkzNzU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/PqCU28dIQay2LXWYdo1dSw--~B/aD0xMDI1O3c9MTUzNjthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/cmmedia.com.tw/bfd7371ee18330c54178dffb3f4acbdb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbzDcx22q9_9uR0IOjwTDEg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjguODA4NTkzNzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPqCU28dIQay2LXWYdo1dSw--~B%2FaD0xMDI1O3c9MTUzNjthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2Fcmmedia.com.tw%2Fbfd7371ee18330c54178dffb3f4acbdb&h=b9ce890c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f6463cfef86046fcec937514b5b11e445ea8881","tid":2433781,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"羽卒平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db6fef1a71db33d903dc1e3379d3f1604b7cffb","tid":2433781,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"翠翠平好柒喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/m